{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1743","heading":"Awards to recognize members of the acquisition workforce","label":"1743 Awards to recognize members of the acquisition workforce","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptII/ch87/schIV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextSection 3 of the Plain Writing Act of 2010, referred to in subsec. (c)(1)(B)(iii), is , which is set out in a note under , Government Organization and Employees.section 3 of Pub. L. 111–274section 301 of Title 5","Prior ProvisionsA prior section 1743, added , , , related to cooperative education program, prior to repeal by , , .Pub. L. 101–510, div. A, title XII, § 1202(a)104 Stat. 1651Pub. L. 108–136, div. A, title VIII, § 834(b)117 Stat. 1551Nov. 5, 1990Nov. 24, 2003"],"amendments":["Prior ProvisionsA prior section 1743, added , , , related to cooperative education program, prior to repeal by , , .Pub. L. 101–510, div. A, title XII, § 1202(a)104 Stat. 1651Pub. L. 108–136, div. A, title VIII, § 834(b)117 Stat. 1551Nov. 5, 1990Nov. 24, 2003"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Establishment","label":"a .—Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An award of not more than $5,000 to such members who use an iterative writing process to document a first-hand account of using independent judgment to overcome an obstacle the member faced while working within the defense acquisition system (as defined in ).section 3001 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An award of not more than $5,000 to such members who make the best use of the flexibilities and authorities granted by the Federal Acquisition Regulation and Department of Defense Instruction 5000.02 (Operation of the Defense Acquisition System).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Number of Awards.—","label":"b Number of Awards.—","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":".—In general","label":"1 .—In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The President of the Defense Acquisition University may make not more than five awards under subsection (a)(1) and one award under subsection (a)(2) each year.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":".—Limitation","label":"2 .—Limitation","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A member of the acquisition workforce may receive one award each year.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Requirements for Writing Award.—","label":"c Requirements for Writing Award.—","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":".—Submission required","label":"1 .—Submission required","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an original and engaging idea documenting the use of independent judgment to overcome an obstacle the recipient faced while working within the defense acquisition system; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"critical thinking;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"incorporation of feedback from diverse perspectives; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"editing to achieve plain writing (as defined in section 3 of the Plain Writing Act of 2010 ( note)).5 U.S.C. 301","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":".—Website","label":"2 .—Website","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs1743%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The President of the Defense Acquisition University shall establish and maintain a website to serve as a repository for submissions made under paragraph (1). Such website shall allow for public comments and discussion.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":".—Requirements for Flexibility Award","label":"d .—Requirements for Flexibility Award","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1743","sourceU